---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Roof Repairs Wilsonton | Reroofing & Insurance Claims"
  description="Roof repairs & reroofing in Wilsonton, Toowoomba — older fibro & metal roofs, replacements, storm & hail damage and insurance-claim work in the western suburbs. QBCC-licensed. Free quote."
  canonical="https://toowoombaroofrepairs.com.au/wilsonton/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Wilsonton &middot; western Toowoomba</span>
      <h1>Roof repairs &amp; reroofing in <span class="accent">Wilsonton</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Wilsonton, in Toowoomba&rsquo;s west, has a lot of older housing stock
        &mdash; ageing fibro and metal roofs that are reaching the point of
        needing replacement rather than another patch. That&rsquo;s where we come
        in: honest advice on repair versus reroof, plus storm and hail damage and
        insurance-claim work. QBCC-licensed.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Wilsonton</span>
      <h2>Roofing the established western suburbs.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Older roofs at the end of their life.</h3>
        <p>
          A good share of Wilsonton&rsquo;s roofs are old enough that repairs are
          becoming a losing game. Older metal roofs rust out at the laps, around
          the fasteners and along the gutter line; once the rust is through the
          sheet rather than just surface, a patch fails again at the next storm.
          When a roof has reached that stage we&rsquo;ll tell you straight that a
          <a href="/services/roof-replacement/">reroof</a> is the better spend
          over the next twenty years &mdash; and we&rsquo;ll show you the photos
          so it&rsquo;s your informed call, not a sales pitch.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Older fibro and asbestos-cement roofs.</h3>
        <p>
          Some of the older homes here still have fibro (asbestos-cement) roof
          sheeting. That material has to be handled and disposed of under strict
          licensed-removal rules &mdash; it is not something to drill, cut or
          pressure-clean. Where a roof involves asbestos-cement we coordinate
          properly with licensed removalists before we fit the new roof, so the
          job is done safely and legally. We&rsquo;ll always flag it if we
          suspect it during the inspection.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Storm damage and insurance claims.</h3>
        <p>
          Like the rest of Toowoomba, Wilsonton sits under the Darling Downs storm
          season, and an older roof is the most vulnerable when the hail and wind
          arrive. Storm and hail damage is generally an insurance matter &mdash;
          we make the roof safe first, then provide the scope and photos your
          assessor needs and deal with them directly. See
          <a href="/services/storm-hail-damage/">storm &amp; hail damage</a> for
          how the claim process works.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Repairs while the roof still has life.</h3>
        <p>
          Not every Wilsonton roof needs replacing &mdash; plenty just need a leak
          chased, a few tiles or sheets sorted, or the ridge capping re-bedded and
          flexible-repointed. Where the roof still has good years left, that&rsquo;s
          exactly what we quote. See our <a href="/services/roof-repairs/">roof
          repairs</a> page for the detail.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Wilsonton jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Honest repair-versus-replace assessment on an ageing metal roof</li>
          <li>Full metal reroof on a rust-perforated older roof ($18K&ndash;$30K)</li>
          <li>Coordinated reroof where old fibro sheeting needs licensed removal first</li>
          <li>Storm and hail damage make-safe and insurance-claim repair</li>
          <li>Leak repair and ridge-cap re-bedding while the roof still has life ($450&ndash;$4,000)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/rangeville/">Rangeville</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/centenary-heights/">Centenary Heights</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/highfields/">Highfields</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/glenvale/">Glenvale</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/toowoomba-region/">All Toowoomba Region</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Wilsonton roof quote.</h2>
        <p>Ageing roof, storm damage, or not sure whether to repair or replace &mdash; we&rsquo;ll get up there and give you the honest answer.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
